### HR Mobile UI Contract API Tests
### Base URL
@hrBaseUrl = http://localhost:5001

### 1. Get Complete Mobile UI Specification
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec

### 2. Get Navigation Structure
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/navigation

### 3. Get Employee List Screen Specification
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec/employee-list

### 4. Get Employee Detail Screen Specification
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec/employee-detail

### 5. Get Employee Form Specification
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec/employee-form

### 6. Health Check
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/health

### 7. Example: How Mobile App Would Use This
### Step 1: Discover mobile-enabled modules from MRS
GET http://localhost:5100/api/modules/mobile

### Step 2: Get HR module metadata (includes mobileUISpecUrl)
GET http://localhost:5100/api/modules/hr

### Step 3: Fetch UI spec from the URL provided in module metadata
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec

### Step 4: Fetch specific screen specs as needed
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/hr/mobile/ui-spec/employee-list

### Step 5: Fetch data using the regular API endpoints
GET {{hrBaseUrl}}/api/employees
